g 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Josh-Klinghoffer-Photo-by-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Josh-Klinghoffer-Photo-by-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Josh-Klinghoffer-Photo-by-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Josh-Klinghoffer-Photo-by-Ethan-Miller_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/red-hot-chili-peppers">红辣椒</a>乐队前吉他手乔什·克林霍夫因涉嫌撞倒行人而被控过失致人死亡和过失罪。</p><p>据<a href="https://variety.com/2024/music/news/red-hot-chili-peppers-josh-klinghoffer-sued-for-wrongful-death-1236066239/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>Variety</i></a>和<a href="https://www.tmz.com/2024/07/10/red-hot-chili-peppers-josh-klinghoffer-sued-wrongful-death-accused-running-over-killing-pedestrian-walking-crosswalk/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>TMZ</i></a>报道，这起事件发生在加利福尼亚州阿罕布拉市，诉讼由 47 岁受害者伊斯雷尔·桑切斯的家人提起。</p><p>该事件发生在 3 月 18 日，诉讼称克林霍夫在驾驶 SUV 时打电话。</p><p>报道还称，当克林霍夫左转时，桑切斯正在一个有标记的十字路口过马路。桑切斯被车撞后伤重不治身亡。</p><p>在分享给<a href="https://pitchfork.com/news/former-red-hot-chili-peppers-guitarist-josh-klinghoffer-facing-wrongful-death-lawsuit/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>Pitchfork</i></a>的一份声明中，克林霍夫的律师安德鲁·B·布雷特勒 (Andrew B. Brettler) 表示：“这是一场悲惨的事故。汽车撞上行人后，乔什立即靠边停车，拨打 911，等待警察和救护车到达。他正在全力配合交通调查。”</p><p>桑切斯家庭的律师尼克·罗利 (Nick Rowley) 向<i>《综艺》杂志</i>声称，他们“手机里有他击杀伊斯雷尔·桑切斯时的视频”。</p><p>他继续说道：“以色列·桑切斯正在去杂货店为家人做汤的路上，却再也没有回家。他所做的一切都是正确的，寻找迎面而来的车辆并遵守行人标志，但悲惨的是，克林霍夫先生在匆忙中打电话，用一辆大型SUV从后面撞死了他。桑切斯一家现在面临着巨大的损失和悲伤。在桑切斯先生及其家人得到问责和伸张正义之前，我们不会停止。”</p><p>克林霍夫于 2009 年至 2019 年在红辣椒队担任吉他手，2020 年，他宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/red-hot-chili-peppers-announce-john-frusciante-is-rejoining-band-2587514">将在 10 年后离开红辣椒队。</a>他后来说<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/josh-klinghoffer-no-hard-feelings-red-hot-chili-peppers-departure-2598495">他和乐队之间没有任何芥蒂。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/red-hot-chili-peppers-john-frusciante-perform-first-time-12-years-2606617#:~:text=He's%20back!&amp;text=Footage%20has%20surfaced%20of%20Red,leaving%20the%20band%20in%202008.&amp;text=In%20December%2C%20the%20band%20announced,subsequently%20replaced%20by%20Josh%20Klinghoffer.">后来他被长期会员约翰·弗鲁西安特 (John Frusciante) 取代。</a></p><p>离开乐队后，克林霍夫一直作为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pearl-jam">Pearl Jam</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/janes-addiction">Jane&#39;s Addiction</a>的巡演成员进行表演。</p><p> <i>NME</i>已联系 Klinghoffer 的代表征求意见。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ex-red-hot-chili-peppers-guitarist-sued-for-wrongful-death-in-driving-accident-3773867">前红辣椒乐队吉他手因车祸过失致人死亡被起诉，</a>他首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
